rgument, but we are passing in a []byte type (h.Sum(nil)) instead. To fix this, we can wrap the []byte type in a bytes.NewReader() call to convert it to an io.Reader type:\n\n```\npriv, err := btckey.GenerateKey(bytes.NewReader(h.Sum(nil)))\n```','\n',char(10)),3,0);
