INSERT INTO contents VALUES(156,replace(replace('Please optimize the email.\r\n\r\nHi Michael,\r\n\r\nI learnt from Steven that you are going to have a meeting with Hunter Amenities. We recently reached out to Hunter China to obtain some certificates, but we had difficulties to get what we need. We hope you could help solve this issue during your meeting with Hunter Canada.\r\n\r\nIn order to sell amenities on marketplaces in China, we need to submit the following documents to the platform. Our purchasing team emailed Christy Duan who is the Area Sales Manager Central China at Hunter to request the following documents of the manufacturer of the Marriott amenities we purchase from Hunter. \r\n\r\nProduction Authorization\r\nCosmetics Registration Certificate\r\nBusiness License\r\nCosmetics Production License\r\n\r\nChristy told us to email her boss Lin Chen, Vice President Sales – Greater China, to requests those documents. Lin replied to our email and told us that their Canada head office informed them that such a request has to be originated from the brand, Marriott International. \r\n\r\n','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace(replace('Hi Michael,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. I wanted to touch base with you regarding your upcoming meeting with Hunter Amenities. I understand that you will be discussing several important matters during this meeting, and I''d like to bring to your attention an issue that our company has recently encountered.\r\n\r\nWe''ve been working to obtain certain certificates from Hunter China to market amenities on platforms in China. Unfortunately, we''ve had some difficulty obtaining the necessary documents from Hunter China. Given your upcoming meeting with Hunter Canada, we were hoping that you could help resolve this issue.\r\n\r\nSpecifically, we need the following documents from the manufacturer of the Marriott amenities that we purchase from Hunter:\r\n\r\n- Production Authorization\r\n- Cosmetics Registration Certificate\r\n- Business License\r\n- Cosmetics Production License\r\n\r\nWe reached out to Christy Duan, Area Sales Manager Central China at Hunter for assistance with obtaining these documents. But she directed us to Lin Chen, Vice President Sales - Greater China, who informed us that the request needs to come from Marriott International, the brand of the amenities in question.\r\n\r\nWe would be grateful if you could raise this issue during your upcoming meeting with Hunter Canada and help us obtain the necessary documents. Thank you for your attention to this matter.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\n[Your Name]','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(157,replace(replace('what do you say when you hear that a colleague is not feeling well\r\n','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace('As an AI language model, I do not have feelings. But, below are a few responses you can use when you hear that a colleague is not feeling well:\n\n1. I''m so sorry to hear that. Is there anything I can do to help?\n2. Please take care of yourself and let me know if there''s anything I can do to support you.\n3. I hope you feel better soon. Please take the time you need to rest and recover.\n4. Would you like me to check in with you later or cover any of your work while you''re out?\n5. If there''s anything you need, don''t hesitate to reach out. We''re all here to support you.','\n',char(10)),1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(158,replace(replace('Please optimize the email.\r\n\r\nThanks for your suggestion on UI optimization. We will update our site accordingly.\r\n\r\nRegarding the email accounts, I was  wondering if you have the Elite Fan and Residence Owner accounts for testing. If not, we will just assume that the function is working. \r\n','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace('Dear [Name], \n\nThank you for providing us with your valuable feedback on UI optimization. We greatly appreciate your input and we will be implementing the necessary changes on our site accordingly. \n\nIn addition, we were hoping to inquire about the availability of the Elite Fan and Residence Owner accounts for testing purposes. If these accounts are not available, we will assume that the function is working correctly. \n\nThank you once again for your assistance and we look forward to your continued support. \n\nBest regards, \n\n[Your Name]','\n',char(10)),1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(159,'Why does the Ritz-Carlton use blue as their brand color','As an AI language model, I do not have access to the specific reasoning behind the Ritz-Carlton''s choice of brand color. However, blue is often associated with a sense of calmness, trustworthiness, and professionalism, which may align with the luxury branding and customer experience that the Ritz-Carlton aims to provide. Additionally, the color blue is commonly associated with the ocean and the sky, both of which are elements of nature that are often associated with luxury and relaxation.',1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(160,replace(replace('Optimize the email below.\r\n\r\nWe prefer not to involve the brand at the moment. We do not want to draw the brand''s attention that our site is not offering the fragrance and bath products. Currently the website has very low traffic and has no orders. The fragrance and bath products have short shelf lives. We do not want to purchase a lot of those products which are likely to expire before we sell them out. We just want to check with the vendor regarding MOQ, costs and lead time first, and see if we can purchase just a few pieces so that we can use them as lucky draw prizes for WeChat marketing campaigns. ','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace('Dear Vendor,\n\nWe are interested in potentially purchasing a small quantity of your fragrance and bath products to use as lucky draw prizes in our WeChat marketing campaigns. As our website currently has low traffic and no orders, we would prefer not to draw attention to our brand by offering these products on our site at this time. Additionally, due to the short shelf lives of these products, we would like to inquire about the minimum order quantity, costs, and lead time before making a purchase. \n\nThank you for your time and assistance.\n\nBest,\n[Your Name]','\n',char(10)),1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(161,replace(replace('Optimize the email below.\r\n\r\nHi Amee,\r\n\r\nThe reason why we ask how we can source the fragrance products is because we do not have many low cost products to do lucky draw campaigns. We prefer not to involve the brand at the moment. We do not want to draw the brand''s attention that our site is not offering the fragrance and bath products. Currently the website has very low traffic and has no orders. The fragrance and bath products have short shelf lives. We do not want to purchase a lot of those products which are likely to expire before we sell them out. We just want to check with the vendor regarding MOQ, costs and lead time first.','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace('Dear Amee,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. I wanted to follow up on our previous conversation regarding sourcing fragrance products for our lucky draw campaigns.\n\nAs you may know, we are currently in need of low-cost products for our promotions. At the moment, we prefer not to involve the brand to avoid drawing attention to the fact that our site doesn''t offer fragrance and bath products. With low traffic and no orders, we want to be cautious with our purchasing decisions.\n\nGiven the short shelf lives of these products, we want to check with the vendor regarding the minimum order quantity, costs, and lead time. This will allow us to make an informed decision without stock sitting on our shelves to expire.\n\nThank you for your time and assistance with this matter. We look forward to hearing back from you soon.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your name]','\n',char(10)),1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(162,replace(replace('Optimize the email below.\r\n\r\nHi Amee,\r\n\r\nThe KEM marketing team in China is going to promote our site on WeChat. We are planning to do a luck draw, but the bath robe is the only product that we think is suitable as the prize. We are wondering if we can purchase some fragrance products or amenities as alternative lucky draw prizes.  \r\n\r\nAt the moment, we prefer not to involve the brand to avoid drawing attention to the fact that the CN site doesn''t offer fragrance products and amenities. With low traffic and no orders, we want to be cautious with our purchasing decisions. Given the short shelf lives of these products, we want to check with the vendor regarding the minimum order quantity, costs, and lead time. This will allow us to make an informed decision without stock sitting on our shelves to expire.\r\n','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace('Dear Amee,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. The KEM marketing team in China is planning to promote our site on WeChat and we are considering doing a lucky draw. Currently, we only have bath robes as a potential prize, but we were wondering if we could purchase fragrance products or amenities as alternative options.\n\nTo avoid drawing attention to the fact that our CN site does not offer these products, we prefer not to involve the brand at this time. With low traffic and no orders, we want to be careful with our purchasing decisions. We also want to consider the short shelf lives of these products and ensure we are making an informed decision. Therefore, we would like to check with the vendor regarding minimum order quantities, costs, and lead times before making a purchase.\n\nThank you for your assistance and guidance on this matter.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]','\n',char(10)),1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(164,replace(replace('Write a response to the following email\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you for your response. Let''s begin preparing the landing page as we need to submit it soon.\r\n\r\nInitially, my goal was to generate 200 incremental orders within 61 days. However, we have now agreed to shorten the campaign days in April (7-17) and focus on promoting 2 hero products with a normal discount offer.\r\n\r\nIn the future, I suggest that we consider the purpose of different campaigns and offer special exclusive discounts on certain channels to maximize the ROI of the campaign. Compared to Tmall and JD, we always get relatively stable traffic. Therefore, our seasonality promotion may not change consumer behavior on Tmall and JD (If you can provide the solid results, please let me know).\r\n\r\nInstead, I propose that we can consider to implement a different pricing strategy on WeChat and other channels during the promotional campaign in the future. I don''t think the discount for the small channel will affect the entire business. After all, we are not an FMCG company.\r\n\r\n','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace('Dear [Name], \n\nThank you for your email. I completely agree that we should start preparing the landing page at the earliest as the deadline is fast approaching. I’ve noted down the change in campaign days and the focus on promoting 2 hero products with a normal discount offer. \n\nI appreciate your suggestion of considering the purpose of different campaigns and offering special exclusive discounts on certain channels to maximize the campaign''s ROI. I will definitely incorporate this in our future planning. \n\nRegarding the seasonality promotion, you have rightly pointed out that we get relatively stable traffic compared to Tmall and JD. I will look into solid results to support this and provide them to you as soon as possible. \n\nI think your idea of a different pricing strategy on WeChat and other channels during the promotional campaign is worth exploring. It certainly sounds like a great way to target a different audience, and I agree it would not affect our entire business. \n\nOnce again, thank you for your email and I look forward to collaborating with you to make this campaign successful. \n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]','\n',char(10)),1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(166,replace(replace('Write another function to allow token login for api according to the following html login function:\r\n\r\nfunc login(c *gin.Context) {\r\n    session := sessions.Default(c)\r\n    db := c.MustGet("db").(*sql.DB)\r\n    username := c.PostForm("username")\r\n    password := c.PostForm("password")\r\n    password = strings.TrimSpace(password)\r\n    var id int \r\n    var dbUsername string\r\n    var dbPassword string\r\n    var role int \r\n    err := db.QueryRow("SELECT id, username, password, role_id FROM users WHERE username=?", username).Scan(&id, &dbUsername, &dbPassword, &role)\r\n    if err != nil {\r\n        log.Println(err)\r\n        c.HTML(http.StatusUnauthorized, "login.tmpl", gin.H{"error": "Invalid user"})\r\n        return\r\n    }   \r\n    if CheckPassword(dbPassword, password) {\r\n        session.Set(userkey, id) \r\n        session.Set(userrole, role)\r\n        if err := session.Save(); err != nil {\r\n            c.HTML(http.StatusInternalServerError, "login.tmpl", gin.H{"error": "Failed to save session"})\r\n            return\r\n        }\r\n        c.HTML(http.StatusOK, "input.tmpl", gin.H{})\r\n    } else {\r\n        c.HTML(http.StatusUnauthorized, "login.tmpl", gin.H{"error": "Invalid password"})\r\n    }\r\n}','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),replace(replace('func tokenLogin(c *gin.Context) {\r\n    db := c.MustGet("db").(*sql.DB)\r\n    username := c.PostForm("username")\r\n    password := c.PostForm("password")\r\n    password = strings.TrimSpace(password)\r\n    var id int \r\n    var dbUsername string\r\n    var dbPassword string\r\n    var role int \r\n    err := db.QueryRow("SELECT id, username, password, role_id FROM users WHERE username=?", username).Scan(&id, &dbUsername, &dbPassword, &role)\r\n    if err != nil {\r\n        log.Println(err)\r\n        c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{"error": "Invalid user"})\r\n        return\r\n    }   \r\n    if CheckPassword(dbPassword, password) {\r\n        token := jwt.New(jwt.SigningMethodHS256)\r\n        claims := token.Claims.(jwt.MapClaims)\r\n        claims["id"] = id\r\n        claims["role"] = role\r\n        tokenString, err := token.SignedString([]byte("my_secret_key"))\r\n        if err != nil {\r\n            c.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, gin.H{"error": "Failed to generate token"})\r\n            return\r\n        }\r\n        c.JSON(http.StatusOK, gin.H{"token": tokenString})\r\n    } else {\r\n        c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{"error": "Invalid password"})\r\n    }\r\n}','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),3,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(167,replace(replace('翻译下面这段话：\r\n\r\nEnter the command in the text box below, such as "Translate the following paragraph into Chinese: Enter the command in the text box below." or "Write an email in French to Mr. Anderson, explaining that due to delivery reasons, his mattress will only be delivered to his home at the end of next month. We apologize for the inconvenience." For guidance on how to create clear and effective prompt guidelines, please refer to the website https://openai.wiki/chatgpt-prompting-guide-book.html.\r\n\r\n','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),'在下方的文本框中输入命令，例如“将以下段落翻译成中文：在下方文本框中输入命令。”或“写一封法语电子邮件给安德森先生，解释由于交货原因，他的床垫只能在下个月末送到他家。为给您带来不便，我们深感抱歉。”如需了解如何编写明确有效的提示指南，请参阅网站https://openai.wiki/chatgpt-prompting-guide-book.html。',1,0);
INSERT INTO contents VALUES(168,'Write a golang function to read the token configuration from .env file',replace('Unfortunately, as an AI language model, I do not have access to system files or functions, and thus cannot provide a functional code for accessing the .env file. However, here is what the basic function could look like:\n\n```go\npackage main\n\nimport (\n    "fmt"\n    "os"\n    "github.com/joho/godotenv"\n)\n\nfunc readTokenConfig() (string, error) {\n    err := godotenv.Load(".env")\n    if err != nil {\n        return "", fmt.Errorf("error getting env variables: %s", err)\n    }\n\n    token := os.Getenv("TOKEN")\n    if token == "" {\n        return "", fmt.Errorf("environment key TOKEN is empty")\n    }\n\n    return token, nil\n}\n```\n\nAssuming that the `TOKEN` value is stored in the `.env` file and accessible through the `os.Getenv` function, the above function should load the `.env` file and read the `TOKEN` value for use in the application.','\n',char(10)),1,0);
